{"tid":282140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SONY宣佈PSN用戶超2640萬","createTime":"2017-06-13T06:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T05:58:54.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"206781b67ae88f014dc5da9c0703b6f45961a14c","tid":282140,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"月費都年收7,80億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n索尼互動娛樂在今天正式宣布，截止到2017年6月11日，旗下 PS4 主機全球累積銷量已達到6040萬，實體版和數字版軟體累計銷量超過4.87億（不含DLC）。<br />\n<br />\n此外，截止到2017年3月底，PlayStation 每月擁有超過7000萬活躍用戶，擁有超過2640萬 PS+ 付費會員，每周活躍用戶的平均使用時間超過6億小時。<br />\n<br />\n對此，索尼互動娛樂總裁 Andrew House 表示：「非常感謝在世界各地一直有持續支持著 PS4 的玩家與合作夥伴。今年除了會有更多精彩的 PS4 遊戲推出之外，我們還將透過擴展 PlayStation VR 的內容以及網絡服務來充實整個 PS4 商業生態系統。索尼將會持續提供最棒的 PS4 娛樂體驗給世界各地的玩家。」"},{"pid":"4100471c16172dca83ce9d6d3a5e6d464e90f377","tid":282140,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"得一半玩家join psn"},{"pid":"f455fdd4fdf9101e18bfe395b3a86856a5224ddb","tid":282140,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得一半玩家join psn</blockquote><br />\n唔join psn玩條柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001e5108d188e55be766352ebe9816ccffd10ded","tid":282140,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"淨係月費都收入過月億，唔怪之每個月送D game越黎越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42bfbadd13c8d89d2cf8b883b914e9e4c37eb53","tid":282140,"uid":39685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"月費根本太高，$10USD 一年就差唔多"},{"pid":"7ae44803a953dd8f237f760c6a9b5855f53f306a","tid":282140,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月費根本太高，$10USD 一年就差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有免費game"},{"pid":"0bb5b550ac33730cf439f7ed1cb147dc44d99436","tid":282140,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月費根本太高，$10USD 一年就差唔多</blockquote><br />\n佢呢年係咁買一年送多一兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894710c0f975c22045245f4ec7e89c5759709af4","tid":282140,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"= 每年都整左一隻賣2640萬隻既game<br />\n平少少咁賣<br />\n其實真係好好搵"},{"pid":"c2323f44f3b7541ada86faf1351cf082ae5fc577","tid":282140,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"其中psvita佔幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448d73e0470b82878f5dfa109ce054b9703fd655","tid":282140,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月費根本太高，$10USD 一年就差唔多</blockquote><br />\n一到大時大節就死server大獲d"},{"pid":"096096e52b0e4fcf7eacc66d839bd266538e1955","tid":282140,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>= 每年都整左一隻賣2640萬隻既game<br />\n平少少咁賣<br />\n其實真係好好搵</blockquote><br />\n哇屌你出咩game 都會所有人買仲勁撚過邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13be9231ae5130bf5a6676021a1b710c65f1d1ff","tid":282140,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>= 每年都整左一隻賣2640萬隻既game<br />\n平少少咁賣<br />\n其實真係好好搵</blockquote><br />\n哇屌你出咩game 都會所有人買仲勁撚過邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多game無買無得連線 唔